  "updated": 1776233491,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69df1f7dec42cd0560e49e50",
      "text": "グレイコード",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230277,
      "updated": 1776230277
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22f70000000000f07be4",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/グレイコード グレイコード]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231159,
      "updated": 1776231166
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22fe0000000000f07be5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231167,
      "updated": 1776231167
    },
    {
      "id": "69df23440000000000a56d53",
      "text": "> [https://gyazo.com/44b9bb2fc0f217724908de3903821081]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231237,
      "updated": 1776231329
    },
    {
      "id": "69df23520000000000a56d55",
      "text": "> [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gray_code Gray code]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231251,
      "updated": 1776231251
    },
    {
      "id": "69df23440000000000a56d54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231237,
      "updated": 1776231237
    },
    {
      "id": "69df1f850000000000f07bbe",
      "text": "二進数表現。隣り合う数とのビットの差分が 1 ビット分になる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230277,
      "updated": 1776231167
    },
    {
      "id": "69df207c0000000000f07bd3",
      "text": "table:gray code",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230525,
      "updated": 1776230531
    },
    {
      "id": "69df1fb70000000000f07bc0",
      "text": "\t0: 0000\t4: 0110\t8: 1100\tC: 1010",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230328,
      "updated": 1776230839
    },
    {
      "id": "69df1fc20000000000f07bc1",
      "text": "\t1: 0001\t5: 0111\t9: 1101\tD: 1011",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230338,
      "updated": 1776230837
    },
    {
      "id": "69df1fc40000000000f07bc2",
      "text": "\t2: 0011\t6: 0101\tA: 1111\tE: 1001",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230341,
      "updated": 1776230836
    },
    {
      "id": "69df1fc70000000000f07bc3",
      "text": "\t3: 0010\t7: 0100\tB: 1110\tF: 1000",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230344,
      "updated": 1776230835
    },
    {
      "id": "69df20360000000000f07bd1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230454,
      "updated": 1776230455
    },
    {
      "id": "69df208e0000000000f07bd4",
      "text": "位取り記数法により二進数を表そうとすると、数値変化の瞬間に数値を誤読する可能性がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230543,
      "updated": 1776230620
    },
    {
      "id": "69df20db0000000000f07bd6",
      "text": "\t例えば 3 から 4 に変わる場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230620,
      "updated": 1776230733
    },
    {
      "id": "69df21440000000000f07bd9",
      "text": " \t3: 011",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230724,
      "updated": 1776230735
    },
    {
      "id": "69df20f30000000000f07bd7",
      "text": " \t4: 100",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230643,
      "updated": 1776230735
    },
    {
      "id": "69df20f90000000000f07bd8",
      "text": " \t3 から 4 に変わる際に全てのビットを同時に変化させるように保証するのが難しい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230649,
      "updated": 1776230911
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22300000000000f07bdb",
      "text": " \t\tビットの変化のズレと読み込みタイミングによって以下の値が取得され得る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230961,
      "updated": 1776231044
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22730000000000f07bdc",
      "text": " \t\t\t000、001、010、011、100、101、110、111",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231027,
      "updated": 1776231028
    },
    {
      "id": "69df228e0000000000f07bdd",
      "text": " \t\t\t……全部やないか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231055,
      "updated": 1776231068
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22010000000000f07bda",
      "text": " \t数値が 1 異なる際には必ず 1 ビットだけ変化するように定められていれば、この類の読み込みエラーは無くなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230914,
      "updated": 1776231080
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22a70000000000f07bde",
      "text": " \t3: 010",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231080,
      "updated": 1776231088
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22b10000000000f07bdf",
      "text": " \t4: 110",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231089,
      "updated": 1776231093
    },
    {
      "id": "69df208e0000000000f07bd5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776230543,
      "updated": 1776230543
    },
    {
      "id": "69df23d20000000000a56d58",
      "text": "論理的な組み合わせを列挙する際にグレイコードを用いると類似する物を隣接させることができる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231379,
      "updated": 1776231418
    },
    {
      "id": "69df256c0000000000a56d66",
      "text": "\t絵の具の混色",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231788,
      "updated": 1776231799
    },
    {
      "id": "69df24a00000000000a56d5e",
      "text": "  ーーー　[$ \\color{#fff}\\bull]白",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231585,
      "updated": 1776232642
    },
    {
      "id": "69df252f0000000000a56d5f",
      "text": "  ーー Y　[$ \\color{#ff0}\\bull]黄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231728,
      "updated": 1776232645
    },
    {
      "id": "69df25320000000000a56d60",
      "text": "  ーM Y　[$ \\color{#f00}\\bull]赤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231730,
      "updated": 1776232646
    },
    {
      "id": "69df25360000000000a56d61",
      "text": "  ーM ー　[$ \\color{#f0f}\\bull]マゼンタ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231734,
      "updated": 1776232651
    },
    {
      "id": "69df25390000000000a56d62",
      "text": "  C M ー　[$ \\color{#00f}\\bull]青",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231737,
      "updated": 1776232654
    },
    {
      "id": "69df253b0000000000a56d63",
      "text": "  C M Y　[$ \\color{#000}\\bull]黒",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231740,
      "updated": 1776232656
    },
    {
      "id": "69df25430000000000a56d64",
      "text": "  C ーY　[$ \\color{#0c0}\\bull]緑",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231747,
      "updated": 1776232658
    },
    {
      "id": "69df25470000000000a56d65",
      "text": "  C ーー　 [$ \\color{#0ff}\\bull]シアン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231751,
      "updated": 1776232663
    },
    {
      "id": "69df24840000000000a56d5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231556,
      "updated": 1776231583
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22ca0000000000f07be0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231114,
      "updated": 1776231114
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22db0000000000f07be2",
      "text": "位取り記数法による二進数[$ x]とグレイコード[$ g]の変換",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231131,
      "updated": 1776231151
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22ee0000000000f07be3",
      "text": "\t[$ g=x\\ {\\rm xor}\\ (x>>1)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231151,
      "updated": 1776232958
    },
    {
      "id": "69df29870000000000a56d67",
      "text": " \t例：6 の変換",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776232840,
      "updated": 1776232982
    },
    {
      "id": "69df29ad0000000000a56d68",
      "text": " \t\t.\t1\t1\t0",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776232877,
      "updated": 1776232982
    },
    {
      "id": "69df29b20000000000a56d69",
      "text": " \t\txor)\t0\t1\t1\t0",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776232883,
      "updated": 1776232982
    },
    {
      "id": "69df29b80000000000a56d6a",
      "text": " \t\t.\t1\t0\t1\t-",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776232888,
      "updated": 1776232982
    },
    {
      "id": "69df29f70000000000a56d6b",
      "text": "\t[$ x=g\\ {\\rm xor}\\ (g>>1)\\ {\\rm xor}\\ (g>>2)\\ {\\rm xor}\\ (g>>3)\\cdots]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776232952,
      "updated": 1776233491
    },
    {
      "id": "69df2b750000000000a56d6d",
      "text": "\t\t.\t1\t0\t1",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776233334,
      "updated": 1776233376
    },
    {
      "id": "69df2b7e0000000000a56d6e",
      "text": "\t\t.\t\t1\t0\t|1",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776233343,
      "updated": 1776233385
    },
    {
      "id": "69df2b830000000000a56d6f",
      "text": "\t\txor)\t\t\t1\t|0\t1",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776233348,
      "updated": 1776233386
    },
    {
      "id": "69df2ba50000000000a56d70",
      "text": "\t\t.\t1\t1\t0\t-\t-",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776233382,
      "updated": 1776233398
    },
    {
      "id": "69df22ca0000000000f07be1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776231114,
      "updated": 1776231114
    }
  ]
}